Re: Bitcoin clients getting k-lined from the IRC bootstrapping channel

Bitcointalk

2010-06-26 14:28:06 UTC - [11]Original Post

   Freenode is too visible, right in the middle of where all those users
   and moderators are hanging out.  Laszloʼs option is a much better fit
   for us.
   I made 0.3.0.RC2 available that uses irc.lfnet.org instead of freenode
   if you want to start switching over:
